title: Final Destination - Spring Break Cancun
description:
Not sure where i pilfered this text from but here is a description... 

A group of college students head to Cancun, Mexico for Spring Break. Their fun and partying is quickly cut short when a hotel fire and subsequent explosion kills hundreds. Only a terrifying premonition by Carly, one of the girls in the group, saves the lives of her and her friends. Against Carly\\\&#039;s warnings the kids decide to stay in Mexico and make the best of their trip. But when Carly\\\&#039;s friends begin to fall victim to horrible \\\&#039;accidents\\\&#039; they soon realize that Death never takes a vacation!
